title: Aurora Literária (A)
body:
A literary journal, of which six issues were published from February 1 to May 1, 1808. It was edited by the students of the lyceum of this city.

Under the same title, another journal was published, of which only six issues were also released, the first on April 2, 1875.

1808: Six issues were published from February 1 to May 1
1875: The first issue was released on April 2
